{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300784, "create_time": 1658114771, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "本科？", "timestamp": 1658114771}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300785, "create_time": 1658114790, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "效仿一下旧洞的拓扑洞和几何洞，不过dz没有那两位dalao那么强", "timestamp": 1658114790}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300787, "create_time": 1658114798, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 是的", "timestamp": 1658114798}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300788, "create_time": 1658114839, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "将来打算出国吗", "timestamp": 1658114839}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300789, "create_time": 1658114992, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 肯定会去国外交流/博后，但会不会呆在国外还要看自己做得怎么样", "timestamp": 1658114992}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300790, "create_time": 1658115083, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "本？硕？博？", "timestamp": 1658115083}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300795, "create_time": 1658115257, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "dz在数论方向主要的兴趣点有哪些呢？", "timestamp": 1658115257}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300804, "create_time": 1658115630, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz认为当前数学领域的前沿关键问题有哪些？", "timestamp": 1658115630}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300806, "create_time": 1658115676, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 大概是代数数论、算术几何吧（虽然我还没怎么学算术几何）；不太明白解析数论的道理，大概也不会特别学习解析数论", "timestamp": 1658115676}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300809, "create_time": 1658115850, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 数论的话，我能想到的问题大概有Riemann猜想，BSD猜想，Langlands纲领，标准猜想；当然计算数论肯定也有很重要的问题，比如素数分解etc，但我就不太了解了", "timestamp": 1658115850}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300812, "create_time": 1658115962, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 当然这些问题之间都有密切的关联", "timestamp": 1658115962}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300822, "create_time": 1658116526, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "大几啊\n", "timestamp": 1658116526}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300825, "create_time": 1658116641, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 具体的就不回答了，以免被猜出来。只能说是本科高年级。", "timestamp": 1658116641}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300831, "create_time": 1658116799, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "从数学的角度，对于机器学习，dz有何看法？", "timestamp": 1658116799}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300836, "create_time": 1658117006, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 啊，这我不了解；可以发邮件问周源或谢丹（雾）", "timestamp": 1658117006}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300866, "create_time": 1658118478, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz平时看数学类期刊或会议文献吗？比较关注哪些期刊或会议？从文献中收获大吗？", "timestamp": 1658118478}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300872, "create_time": 1658118991, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: dz不怎么看期刊，还处在读古老文献的阶段。看已经开始做研究的dalao，其读期刊的方法大概是在arxiv上冲浪。", "timestamp": 1658118991}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300887, "create_time": 1658119757, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz能否用自然语言说出本系内学长或前辈做出过哪些有真正价值工作？", "timestamp": 1658119757}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300905, "create_time": 1658120716, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 什么叫有真正价值呢？实话实说纯数确实没太多应用……如果是要列举一些清华毕业的，在自己方向做得很出色的人，那还是有的，比如单芃老师、吴昊老师（我怎么只能说出这两个，还都是学姐，看来清华若干年前确实远不如北大）", "timestamp": 1658120716}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300913, "create_time": 1658121016, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 也有可能很多人都润去国外了，所以我不了解", "timestamp": 1658121016}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300916, "create_time": 1658121151, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "纯数研究的主要方法论是什么（和不限时长的做题的最大区别是什么呢", "timestamp": 1658121151}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300926, "create_time": 1658122045, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 我个人的看法是，纯数研究的目的不是为了解题，而是为了更好地“理解”一些事情。中学乃至大学中，竞赛或考试类的解题，我们的主要解题手段是“绕过”题目的困难所在，而研究就是要直面这些困难。最直接的例子，是数学中种种分类定理。从Grothendieck之后，数学家也热衷于“造轮子”，动辄建立庞大的体系以解决某些问题。我来贴一段格的话，大概可以表明我欣赏而仰慕的一种数学风格：\n", "timestamp": 1658122045}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300927, "create_time": 1658122055, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "每一门科学，当我们不是将它作为能力和统治力的工具，而是作为我们人类世代以来努力追求的对知识的冒险历程，不是别的，就是这样一种和谐，从一个时期到另一个时期，或多或少，巨大而又丰富：在不同的时代和世纪中，对于依次出现的不同的主题，它展现给我们微妙而精细的对应，仿佛来自虚空", "timestamp": 1658122055}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300930, "create_time": 1658122397, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 不错的想法。不过dz没有直接回答方法论呢。譬如dz现在要处理一个问题，dz要做的是不断试以前的轮子看看用不用的上，要是都不行就尝试将两个轮子拼在一起，再不行就等灵感爆发吗？", "timestamp": 1658122397}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300936, "create_time": 1658122799, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 对，是这样的。以及方法论中还有重要的一环是算例子，从简单到复杂，这也是为了加深理解。", "timestamp": 1658122799}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300939, "create_time": 1658122907, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 好的，感谢dz的解答", "timestamp": 1658122907}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300940, "create_time": 1658122939, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 有时候也可能是水到渠成，但这都是大师才能做到的了。Serre说他写FAC（代数几何中重要的论文，将层论引入代数几何）时，感觉像是在写一篇已经有的东西，而他只是在复述。", "timestamp": 1658122939}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300946, "create_time": 1658123114, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz对工科生的看法是？（比如贵系 雷系）", "timestamp": 1658123114}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300953, "create_time": 1658123367, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz本科阶段的培养计划中学习编程吗？何种编程语言？", "timestamp": 1658123367}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300956, "create_time": 1658123742, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 我程序设计（培养计划中的）学得很差，所以觉得擅长编程是一件很cool的事情。如果有空的话，可能会看看Haskell, HoTT之类的东西", "timestamp": 1658123742}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300959, "create_time": 1658124009, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: 想问下洞主，代数几何大概是在干", "timestamp": 1658124009}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300967, "create_time": 1658124193, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果想初步体会到其中的有趣的东西，对于只会非数学专业的微积分线代概率论拓扑的人，有没有什么极简的学习路径", "timestamp": 1658124193}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300990, "create_time": 1658124628, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 代数几何也有很多分支，最古典正统意义的代数几何是双有理几何，研究代数封闭域上的代数簇在双有理意义下的分类。现在（在名词党/本科生代数几何学家中）最流行的是算术几何，它研究数域或有限域上的代数簇，各种fancy的概念和名词基本都是这里来的。", "timestamp": 1658124628}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 300999, "create_time": 1658124952, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 现代的代数几何严重依赖于代数语言，如果没学过抽象代数乃至交换代数可能不太容易理解。不过，黎曼面中已经蕴含了很多代数几何中的道理。你大概可以看一下关于黎曼面的教材，比如GTM 81，也顺道复习复分析和拓扑。", "timestamp": 1658124952}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301010, "create_time": 1658125365, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "求问洞主有没有推荐的科普书呢？（来自一个工科打工人，下班后想看点闲书", "timestamp": 1658125365}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301016, "create_time": 1658125576, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz怎么评价工科生的数学水平？", "timestamp": 1658125576}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301027, "create_time": 1658126048, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Hans:  西蒙﹒辛格的《费马大定理》，可以当故事书来看，同样的还有《我的几何人生》（大雾）。教材性质的有Tate&Silverman写的《椭圆曲线上的有理点》，它是讲座整理而来，面向数学系本科生平均水平（作者序言中宣称），所以叙述流畅而初等。另外很多人推荐侯世达的GEB(哥德尔，埃舍尔，巴赫），不过我没读过。", "timestamp": 1658126048}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301029, "create_time": 1658126169, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re 洞主: 谢谢洞主的用心推荐！", "timestamp": 1658126169}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301034, "create_time": 1658126305, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 不了解，但能达到培养计划要求的不就够了么，又不是所有人都要深入学习数学，就像不需要人们都钢琴十级一样，，，", "timestamp": 1658126305}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301206, "create_time": 1658130839, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "xs已经猜到了", "timestamp": 1658130839}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301207, "create_time": 1658130872, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "dz信息太多了，“程序设计很差”一下子就猜到了", "timestamp": 1658130872}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301227, "create_time": 1658131413, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "谢谢洞主！", "timestamp": 1658131413}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301295, "create_time": 1658133332, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "dz觉得Riemann猜想的彻底解决还要多远", "timestamp": 1658133332}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301311, "create_time": 1658133992, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Isabella: 那通过这个猜到，还是有猜错的可能", "timestamp": 1658133992}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301312, "create_time": 1658134048, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Jason: 感觉广义黎曼猜想大概有生之年都不能见到解决", "timestamp": 1658134048}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 301898, "create_time": 1658157509, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "dz最喜欢的几位数学家是？", "timestamp": 1658157509}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 302301, "create_time": 1658193887, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: Grothendieck", "timestamp": 1658193887}], "create_time": 1658114738, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658193887, "likenum": 17, "n_attentions": 17, "n_comments": 47, "pid": 84889, "poll": null, "reply": 47, "text": "问答洞，dz是数学系（想学）数论方向的，感兴趣的dy可以提问", "timestamp": 1658114738}}